02:38.558 --> 02:39.957
- All right, hold it, hold it.
- Right.

02:40.093 --> 02:41.390
Of course, I'm alive.

02:41.528 --> 02:43.360
Just a little
gasoline explosion.

02:43.497 --> 02:44.965
Gasoline explosion nothing.

02:45.098 --> 02:46.566
Those counterfeiters are trying
