02:53.006 --> 02:54.030
All right.

02:54.174 --> 02:55.403
- I overheard them, Fonz.
- Yeah?

02:55.542 --> 02:57.601
And you know the Candy Man,
the...

02:57.744 --> 02:59.007
- Yeah.
- And the other, the...

02:59.146 --> 03:00.409
-and-and the tall...
- Yeah.

03:00.547 --> 03:02.743
They know that-that you took
the money out of the coffin

03:02.883 --> 03:04.442
and they're trying
to silence you, Fonz.

03:04.584 --> 03:06.052
I mean, they're trying
to silence you for good.

03:06.186 --> 03:07.483
All right, all right.
They hushed me.

03:07.621 --> 03:08.679
They didn't silence me.

03:08.822 --> 03:10.586
How in the world did you
even survive this?

03:10.724 --> 03:12.283
Well, because at the time
of the explosion,

03:12.426 --> 03:14.588
I was behind
my address book, whoa.

03:14.728 --> 03:16.492
Yeah, whoa and...
(imitates explosion)

03:16.630 --> 03:18.462
Yes. Hey, Richie.

03:18.598 --> 03:19.929
- Yeah.
- Let me tell you something.

03:20.067 --> 03:23.162
Those guys are beginning to make
me a little angry, you know?

03:31.812 --> 03:33.803
