03:45.425 --> 03:46.688
(imitates explosion)

03:46.827 --> 03:48.090
Fonzarelli the mechanic

03:48.228 --> 03:50.322
is now at the corner
of Fourth and Main.

03:50.464 --> 03:51.795
And Fifth and Main,

03:51.932 --> 03:53.263
and Sixth and Main.

03:53.400 --> 03:54.595
Now listen carefully.

03:54.735 --> 03:56.760
I want you to go
to the secret room,

03:56.903 --> 04:00.840
get those two clowns we tied up
and have them call home.

04:08.682 --> 04:10.241
We're going to let
you boys call home

04:10.383 --> 04:11.748
so your folks don't worry.

04:11.885 --> 04:13.910
The Candy Man doesn't
want anybody to miss you

04:14.054 --> 04:16.079
and come nosing around here.

04:16.223 --> 04:18.817
You do want to go home,
don't you?

04:18.959 --> 04:21.257
Oh, sure,
my father'll probably talk to me

04:21.394 --> 04:22.486
since I'm all tied up.

04:22.629 --> 04:23.619
I'll call home.

04:23.764 --> 04:25.391
My mother worries
if I stay out late.

04:25.532 --> 04:27.125
What's your name, kid?

04:27.267 --> 04:28.996
Cunningham.

04:29.136 --> 04:30.661
Ralph Cunningham.

04:33.840 --> 04:35.239
