one extra hour tonight!

24:00.773 --> 24:03.140
(cheering)

24:03.275 --> 24:05.073
- Hey, Rich.
- Hmm?

24:05.210 --> 24:07.975
Want to tell me the part about
how you captured the Candy Man?

24:08.113 --> 24:10.514
Well, I didn't, you know...

24:10.649 --> 24:13.482
Why don't we talk about it
at Inspiration Point?

24:13.619 --> 24:14.814
- Hey, Jennifer.
- Hmm?

24:14.954 --> 24:16.388
Jennifer, let's you and I go

24:16.522 --> 24:17.648
