24:17.790 --> 24:19.258
Oh, good idea, Potsie.

24:19.391 --> 24:21.883
Yeah, you can tie me up,
and I'll show you how I escaped.

24:22.895 --> 24:23.919
What about me?

24:24.063 --> 24:25.053
I was there, too.

24:25.197 --> 24:26.562
Joanie, Joanie,
don't you want to hear

24:26.699 --> 24:28.258
